/** `heddle undo --list --output json` history view. Distinct from [`UndoSchema`] (the rewind/redo payload): the list view carries only the discriminator and the oplog batches, with none of the action/status/ recovery fields a real undo emits. Mirrors `OpListOutput` in `undo.rs`. */
